This package will install some additional searchproviders for greek sites,
to use with Konqueror and KRunner.

Searchproviders are:

  skroutz:
      Search for prices using skroutz.gr
      e.g., shop:nexus => http://www.skroutz.gr/search?keyphrase=nexus

  ufgr:
      Search in forum.ubuntu-gr.org
      e.g., ufgr:gimp => http://forum.ubuntu-gr.org/search.php?keywords=gimp
